OL,3,CMan arrested after 87-year-old beaten
OL,4,Cand dumped 15 miles away in Yorkshire
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof kidnap after a pensioner was
OL,8,Fbundled into a car and thrown out in
OL,9,FWest Yorkshire.
OL,11,FThe 87-year-old was reportedly dragged
OL,12,Finto a black car on Lee Street,
OL,13,FOldham, before being driven to West
OL,14,FYorkshire between 9 and 9.30pm on
OL,15,FSunday 15 September.
OL,17,FHe was attacked on the way, suffering
OL,18,Fserious injuries. He eventually found
OL,19,Faid by knocking on a door at around
OL,20,F10.40pm.
