OL,3,CMan arrested after 87-year-old beaten
OL,4,Cand dumped 15 miles away in Yorkshire
OL,6,FA 39-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of kidnap and remains in
OL,8,Fcustody for questioning.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Emma Hulston, from
OL,11,FGMP's Major Incident Team, said: "We
OL,12,Fare still establishing the full
OL,13,Fcircumstances of this horrendous
OL,14,Fincident, including putting together
OL,15,Fan exact timeline that led to the man
OL,16,Fbeing attacked and thrown from the car
OL,17,Fmiles from his home.
