OL,6,F"While this is obviously a shocking
OL,7,Fincident for the local community, we
OL,8,Fdo currently believe that this is an
OL,9,Fisolated incident with no wider threat
OL,10,Fto the public.
OL,12,F"We are still appealing for
OL,13,Finformation in relation to the
OL,14,Finvestigation and I would urge anyone
OL,15,Fwho may know something that could
OL,16,Fassist to please get in touch.
OL,18,F"This includes anyone who may have
OL,19,Fpossession of the relevant CCTV,
OL,20,Fdashcam, or doorbell footage."
