OL,7,Fopened a major incident portal for
OL,8,Finformation to be submitted to, as
OL,9,Fthey continue their enquiries.
OL,11,FYou can contact the incident room
OL,12,Fdirectly by calling 0161 856 3635 or
OL,13,FGMP via 101 or gmp.police.uk, quoting
OL,14,Flog 3165 of 15/09/24.
OL,16,FIf contacting from West Yorkshire, you
OL,17,Fcan contact West Yorkshire Police via
OL,18,F101, quoting log 1730 of 15/09/24.
